with tempfile.TemporaryDirectory() as dirname:
    with open(pkg_resources.resource_filename(__name__, PROFILE_FILE)) as f:
        profile = json.load(f)
    make_resume_files(profile, dirname, TIMEOUT)
    for filename in os.listdir(pkg_resources.resource_filename(__name__,
        RESUME_DIR)):
        assert filecmp.cmp(os.path.join(dirname, RESUME_DIR, filename),
            pkg_resources.resource_filename(__name__,
            f'{RESUME_DIR}/{filename}'), shallow=False) is True
